{"name": "odoo-addon-product-packaging-level-salable", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-product-packaging-level-salable", "version": "16.0.1.0.0.6", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo-addon-product-packaging-level", "odoo"], "summary": "Product Packaging level salable", "upload_time": 1705729150}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Alpha-red.png\n    :alt: Alpha\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fproduct--attribute-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/product-attribute\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/16.0/product_packaging_level_salable\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/product-attribute-16-0/product-attribute-16-0-product_packaging_level_salable\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/product-attribute&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Product Packaging level salable\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:61bda16403c5ed0955f5cfb90d448b1dfaf08f081948df0411a3b93b3e2035ca\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThe creation/update of sale order line will be blocked (by constraints) if the data on the\nsale.order.line does not fit with the configuration of the product's packagings.\n\n:::{IMPORTANT}\nThis is an alpha version, the data model and design can change at any time without warning.\nOnly for development or testing purpose, do not use in production.\n[More details on development status](https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status)\n:::\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nThis module allows odoo users to set:\n\n- Can be sold: On product packaging level model, this checkbox defines if product\n  packagings from this particular type are available to be selected on sale\n  order line.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/issues/new?body=module:%20product_packaging_level_salable%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Duong (Tran Quoc) \\<<mailto:duongtq@trobz.com>>\n\n### Other credits\n\nThe development of this module has been financially supported by:\n\n- Camptocamp\n\nThis module feature was extracted from the original [sale-workflow/sale_by_packaging](https://github.com/oca/sale-workflow/tree/14.0/sale_by_packaging) module.\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/product-attribute](https://github.com/OCA/product-attribute/tree/16.0/product_packaging_level_salable) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models.product_packaging_level", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 Camptocamp SA", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models.product_packaging_level.ProductPackagingLevel", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models.product_packaging_level.ProductPackagingLevel._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models.product_packaging_level.ProductPackagingLevel.can_be_sold", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models.product_packaging_level.ProductPackagingLevel.packaging_ids", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models.product_packaging", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models..product_packaging", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_packaging_level_salable.models.product_pa